      <Item ItemId=";Docker_PSDescription" ItemType="0" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[The Docker (Linux Container) connection type allows Visual Studio to connect to Docker containers running locally or remotely (using SSH).]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[O tipo de conexão do Docker (Contêiner do Linux) permite que Visual Studio se conecte a contêineres do Docker sendo executados local ou remotamente (usando SSH).]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
          <Prev Cat="Text">
            <Val><![CDATA[Docker Transport allows connecting Visual Studio to Docker containers locally or through SSH.]]></Val>
          </Prev>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
